name: Plane-Wars
description: It's up to you to destroy the f-18 fighter jet... with an old pistol plane. Avoid making contact with red planes, Rockets, mini-Jets, shooter planes and of course, dodge attacks from the F-18 jet at the end. You get 1000 hp, get health box to refill your health points. (Don't go diving after a health box when you have full health). Can you beat the F-18 boss fighter plane? Depends on you and your old broken pistol plane.
